the weekly report in person...

784
01:12:12,546 --> 01:12:14,882
Fine. Then let's have it half and half.

785
01:12:19,929 --> 01:12:22,640
What are you doing, Mom?
Are you receiving an award?

786
01:12:24,058 --> 01:12:24,892
Well...

787
01:12:25,893 --> 01:12:28,688
I had to bring him
because I couldn't find a babysitter.

788
01:12:30,022 --> 01:12:32,566
Who are you, mister?

789
01:12:36,654 --> 01:12:37,697
Nice to meet you.

790
01:12:38,698 --> 01:12:40,992
I am the King of the Kingdom of Corea.

791
01:12:41,575 --> 01:12:43,661
My name is Lee Gon.

